snippet.title: NeoDuel: Backpack Monsters | Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Your Next Strategy Game Obsession: NeoDuel: Backpack Monsters Launches on Steam on September 30th!

Master your Cosmions and dominate the Duel arenas in this monster-taming, inventory management auto-battler. 

Play the DEMO & Wishlist on Steam 👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2693940/

Follow us on social media and our official website as well via:

NeoDuel on Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlayNeoDuel
